{{!< default}}
{{!-- People page. Static team list + careers/Academy preview section.
    Assigned to the /people/ Ghost Page via Page Settings → Template.

    To add or edit team members: edit this template directly. Each .person
    block is one person.
--}}

{{#page}}
<section class="section">
  <div class="reveal" style="margin-bottom: 56px;">
    <div class="eyebrow">People</div>
    <h1 class="display">The hands on the <em>tiller.</em></h1>
    <p class="deck" style="margin-top: 16px; max-width: 52ch;">
      The group is owned by three; governed by five trustees; run by a senior management team across the trading subsidiaries.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="people-grid reveal">

    <div class="person">
      <div class="person-portrait"></div>
      <div class="role">Chair · AMPM Group</div>
      <div class="name">Jamie Dawson</div>
      <div class="note">Strategic lead across the group. Co-owner of AMPM Group Limited. Twenty years with Gemini AMPM.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="person">
      <div class="person-portrait"></div>
      <div class="role">Managing Director · AMPM Group</div>
      <div class="name">Dan Small</div>
      <div class="note">Operational lead across the group. MD remit covers Gemini AMPM and the wider trading subsidiaries as they stand up.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="person">
      <div class="person-portrait"></div>
      <div class="role">Commercial Director · AMPM Group</div>
      <div class="name">Luke Finney</div>
      <div class="note">Group commercial lead. Co-owner of AMPM Group Limited. Twenty years with Gemini AMPM. EOT trustee.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="person">
      <div class="person-portrait"></div>
      <div class="role">EOT Trustee · Sales</div>
      <div class="name">Paul Fitzpatrick</div>
      <div class="note">Independently developed the compliance hub and chatbot — now folded into the AMPM Live platform roadmap as the AI assistant layer.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="person">
      <div class="person-portrait"></div>
      <div class="role">EOT Trustee · Passive Manager</div>
      <div class="name">Lee Woodford</div>
      <div class="note">Operational depth in passive fire — one of the highest-margin life-safety lines.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="person">
      <div class="person-portrait"></div>
      <div class="role">EOT Trustee</div>
      <div class="name">Jozef Markaj</div>
      <div class="note">Trustee of the Gemini AMPM EOT alongside L. Finney, B. Dawson, L. Woodford, P. Fitzpatrick.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="person">
      <div class="person-portrait"></div>
      <div class="role">EOT Director · Trustee</div>
      <div class="name">Bailey Dawson</div>
      <div class="note">Trustee of the Gemini AMPM EOT and director of the EOT corporate trustee.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="person">
      <div class="person-portrait"></div>
      <div class="role">Projects Director · Gemini AMPM</div>
      <div class="name">Ryan Gemmel</div>
      <div class="note">Projects lead. Owner of the technical-drawings AI use case under AMPM Live Intelligence.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="person">
      <div class="person-portrait"></div>
      <div class="role">Management Accountant</div>
      <div class="name">Joe Isaac</div>
      <div class="note">Xero lead. Owner of the credit-control automation use case under AMPM Live Intelligence.</div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="careers reveal">
    <div class="careers-head">
      <div class="eyebrow">Academy · Careers · Growth</div>
      <h2 class="display" style="font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 56px);">Growing the <em>next layer.</em></h2>
      <p class="deck" style="margin-top: 16px; max-width: 60ch;">
        The Academy is both an external training arm and the group's people pipeline. Apprenticeships across the trades, skills training for engineers progressing toward chartership, professional development on the commercial and admin side, and accreditation pathways shared with operators across the sector.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="careers-grid">
      <div class="careers-card">
        <div class="careers-n">01</div>
        <h4>Apprenticeships</h4>
        <p>Fire engineering, security systems, M&amp;E and passive-fire apprenticeships. Earn-as-you-learn pathways into the group's trading subsidiaries. Recruitment opens annually from late summer.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="careers-card">
        <div class="careers-n">02</div>
        <h4>Skills training · trades</h4>
        <p>Accredited courses across fire detection, suppression, compartmentation surveying and gas systems. Sold to engineers across the wider sector; subsidised internally for AMPM staff.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="careers-card">
        <div class="careers-n">03</div>
        <h4>Professional development · office</h4>
        <p>Commercial, project-management, finance and compliance tracks for the office floor. Designed around the operating stack the group actually runs on — Uptick, Procore, M365 — not generic theory.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="careers-card">
        <div class="careers-n">04</div>
        <h4>Accreditation pathways</h4>
        <p>Structured routes toward FIA, BAFE, FIRAS, NICEIC and IFE chartership. The Academy holds the audit framework; engineers progress against it on the job, evidenced in Uptick.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="careers-foot">
      <div>
        <div class="lbl">Open roles &amp; apprenticeships</div>
        <div class="val">careers@ampm.co.uk</div>
      </div>
      <div class="careers-note">
        The Academy's external training prospectus opens for enrolment from Q3 2027. Internal apprenticeships and skills tracks run continuously inside Gemini AMPM today, ahead of the Academy standing up as its own trading entity.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{{!-- Optional editable section from the Page body --}}
{{#if content}}
<section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
  <div class="prose reveal">{{content}}</div>
</section>
{{/if}}
{{/page}}
